         <h1>
            About The Rex
         </h1>
         <h2>
            History
         </h2>
         <p>
            The Rex was first built in 1934. It prospered for many decades before declining in
            popularity and then closing in 1988.
         </p>
         <h2>
            Restoration
         </h2>
         <p>
            Between 1998 and 2004 the Rex underwent a restoration costing &pound;1 million. The Rex
            re-opened its doors to the public in 2004, with three sell out shows in the first two
            weeks.
         </p>
